{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Navy, at that point, had a system of getting people out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a certain number of points.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the married men automatically got more points than a single man, which is perfectly honest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no objections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as a single man, I had to serve, I think, four months longer before I would be eligible for release.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thought-- and he-- and Dostert told me, and he says, if you go to Nuremberg, you're not going to get out after any four months.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, you're going to have to sign up for as long in the Navy as it takes to finish the job at Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, all right, I'll do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I want so badly to see the end of this goddamned thing that I'll sacrifice whatever-- two, three, five months, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, god no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was Lieutenant Commander.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't I tell you about that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At every point in the Navy, for the reserves and those [INAUDIBLE], after about a year and a half of satisfactory, they push you up a grade, see?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got to be a Lieutenant Junior grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I got to be Lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's a-- it came with the Captain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, promotion stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I would-- people would come to me and say, listen-- the next-- by the next promotion would be to Lieutenant Commander, and that would be the first time that the Navy's famous selection board would cut in and choose me, specifically, by-- on my record for promotion.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- Navy-wide, not depending on some commanding officer that you'd boot-licked, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way the Army did it, but not the Navy.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
